snippet.title: EVAVERSE Hoverboard Racing Trailer
snippet.description:
Hoverboard Racing is coming to the Evaverse! 

Each NFT will be airdropped to holders in the EVA community. Racing will be the start of competitive gaming within the Evaverse and ultimately the first fully immersive play-to-earn game mode!
